genresAdvancedInfo.name: uzbek hip hop
genresAdvancedInfo.description: Uzbek hip hop is a relatively new genre in Uzbekistan, blending traditional Uzbek music with elements of hip hop and rap. The lyrics often address social and political issues, as well as personal experiences and struggles. The music is popular among young people in Uzbekistan and has gained a following both locally and internationally.
